data.description: Recently remodeled very nice house in convenient location close to schools & shopping center. Bright Living and Family rooms with fireplace, beautiful kitchen with a lot of space and cabinets, granite countertops, new Kitchen Aid appliances stay, pantry, large Dining room. Master Bedroom with sliding door to deck, 72 inches deep soaking tub, 5 bedrooms with extra large deep closets, extra bonus & mud room. Laminate flooring through all house, new furnace, water heater and insulation in attic and crawl space. Huge covered porch, fully fenced nice big property with gate, RV, boat parking, lots of parking space. Must see.
